{"tid":1922114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實CCTV真係好難應付","createTime":"2020-03-12T11:21:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T11:25:24.000Z","uid":131157,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4c0ddb2b1c1bf20017fffe4e48466399cd32ab73","tid":1922114,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:21:59.000Z","msg":"有團體在1月19日發起在中環遮打花園集會，集會進行大約2小時，警方指因現場出現暴力情況，要求終止集會，及後有警員受到襲擊。警方以有意圖傷人及非法集結罪，拘捕7名年齡介乎13至34的本地男子。<br />\n<br />\n毒品調查科警司鄒旺忠說，當時現場十分混亂，涉及的人數很多，有關人士蒙面及身穿黑衣，令調查困難，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警方要翻看大量片段，包括現場錄影片段及周邊閉路電視片段，強調有足夠證據顯示7名被捕人，有涉嫌直接或間接襲擊警務人員。<br />\n<br />\n鄒旺忠說，在追蹤疑犯逃跑過程中，商戶及一些交通工具營運者有提供片段。被問到是否代表港鐵及巴士公司有提供片段</span></strong>，他說，調查範圍廣闊，不會透露細節，警方不會放過沿路所有線索。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，7名被捕人中有6人是20歲以下，除了最紀最輕的13歲被捕人獲准保釋外，其他人都正被扣查，稍後可能被落案檢控。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想專登開個post 俾大家討論下發夢點應付呢樣野，暫時諗到：<br />\n<br />\n1. 由屋企出門口至番屋企期間，唔好用任何電子付費工具搭車或買野e.g 8達通<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.前線既盡量唔好直接番屋企，搭多幾轉車遊下車河，並要提防便衣狗跟蹤，留意附近同車既CCTV；<br />\n有行開山既可以經山路走，起碼冇cctv<br />\n<br />\n3.有份做野既當日既衣著唔好再留低，俾差役搜屋呢d 會變為呈堂證據<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多係肯定要做既，其他等大家係下邊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513986-20200312.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513986-20200312.htm&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=9733732f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513986-20200312.htm&h=fcf14401\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513986-20200312.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5ecd2f9f466a815c9bb200c2d39dbf0502f2cf91","tid":1922114,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:26:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8fc03d15db5c7193ea1faa13ccb552c4f2f86f48","tid":1922114,"uid":235374,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53e8becaef1a0e4d628dd9887c838fff93b7c17","tid":1922114,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5afb430028a1e87ebb0305c133bd627f842958ce","tid":1922114,"uid":131157,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:27:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">4.前線既做完野達到目的好走，唔好戀戰攪遮陣係現場逗留，愈留係現場愈容易留低證據</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2b5411c969746fba24e8dbe819239e2805d406","tid":1922114,"uid":255313,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:29:44.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n其實咩係間接襲擊警務人員？<br />\n點樣可以唔直接咁襲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880fff433906c65b13ef797d492121250bc44910","tid":1922114,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:29:47.000Z","msg":"ecm 流動電磁波干擾器<br />\n<br />\n我講左咩自己領悟下"},{"pid":"8edf2c2470ece85bd27131688077f4dd81816e69","tid":1922114,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:50:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.g